<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2>New Order - #<%= @order.id %></h2>
    <p>Vendor: <%= @vendor.name %>
    <hr/>
    <p><span style="font-weight: bold">Amount Collected From Customer:</span> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', @order.price) %></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: bold">Amount Alloted for Vendor:</span> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', ((@order.price - ENV["SERVO_SERVICE_CHARGE"].to_f) * (1 - ENV["SERVO_VENDOR_COMMISSION"].to_f))) %></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: bold">Gross Revenue:</span> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', ((@order.price - ENV["SERVO_SERVICE_CHARGE"].to_f) * ENV["SERVO_VENDOR_COMMISSION"].to_f) + ENV["SERVO_SERVICE_CHARGE"].to_f) %></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: bold">Transaction Fee:</span> -$<%= sprintf('%.2f', ((@order.price) * 0.029) + 0.3) %></p>
    <p><span style="font-weight: bold">Profit:</span> $<%= sprintf('%.2f', (((@order.price - ENV["SERVO_SERVICE_CHARGE"].to_f) * ENV["SERVO_VENDOR_COMMISSION"].to_f) + ENV["SERVO_SERVICE_CHARGE"].to_f) - (((@order.price) * 0.029) + 0.3)) %></p> 
    <hr/>
    <p>The attached work order has been sent to the service provider</p>
    <p style="font-size: 10px">You are living life you used to dream of.</p>
  </body>
</html>